	=09
				<h1>Clay Shrinkage Calculator</h1>
	=09
				<p>
					=09
			Calculate how large your pottery piece should be based on how much=20
			your clay shrinks as it dries and is bisque and glaze fired*. Enter your=
=20
			clay's shrink rate, and the desired final dimensions. Also helpful for=
=20
			making replacement lids!
		</p>
		=09
			=09
								<div class=3D"center_region">
			<p>
				<a href=3D"https://photopottery.com/hump-mold.php?id=3D150">
					Pottery Molds - plates and more...=20
				</a>
			</p>
		</div>
		=09
	=09
	<div class=3D"content_section formregion">
	=09
		<form id=3D"frm1" name=3D"frm1" method=3D"POST" action=3D"https://photopo=
ttery.com/clay-shrinkage-calculator.php">
